<author>mạykl ạ̹sḥạq, mạykl ạ̹sḥạq</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ḥbytny wạ̉nạ mạtḥbsẖ wqblt ạ̹nk tlqạny
 wạ̉tgẖyr ḥạly wqlby wbqyt skny wʿnwạny
 1- bạlnʿmẗ ạ̉nạ mtkẖlṣ bmḥbẗ kbyrẗ qwyẗ
 wlsẖkẖṣk ạ̉nạ mtkẖṣṣ tʿml mạ bdạlk by
 2- fy ạlʿạlm knt ạ̉nạ ʿạysẖ mtạkẖd fy ạldwạmẗ
 wạ̉mạ ạ̉ḥb ạ̹ny ạ̉ṣrkẖ ạ̹blys ḥạṭṭ kmạmẗ
 3- qlt lk ạbʿd ʿny wṭryqk msẖ ʿạyz ạ̉msẖyh
 lqytk jyt wnạdyty wṣlybk ḍmạny fyh
 4- bʿd mạ gẖyrt ly qlby hạsẖhd lk ạ̹nk rby
 qlbk ṭyb wbysạʿ mhmạ ạ̹n kạn kbyr dẖnby</lyrics>
<title>ḥbytny̱ wạ̉nạ mạtḥbsẖ</title>
</song>